defines.define: min(x,y) = if x < y then x else y
max(x,y) = if x > y then x else y
abs(x) = if x < 0 then -x else x

rules.rule: operatingTime = if secondTick then operatingTime + 1 else operatingTime
operatingHours = if hourTick then operatingHours + 1 else operatingHours
X11_DI1 = if (X11_DI1 != X11_DI1_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI1_RAW else X11_DI1
X11_DI2 = if (X11_DI2 != X11_DI2_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI2_RAW else X11_DI2

X11_DI7 = if (X11_DI7 != X11_DI7_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI7_RAW else X11_DI7
X11_DI8 = if (X11_DI8 != X11_DI8_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI8_RAW else X11_DI8
X11_DI9 = if (X11_DI9 != X11_DI9_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI9_RAW else X11_DI9
X11_DI10 = if (X11_DI10 != X11_DI10_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI10_RAW else X11_DI10
X11_DI11 = if (X11_DI11 != X11_DI11_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI11_RAW else X11_DI11
X11_DI12 = if (X11_DI12 != X11_DI12_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI12_RAW else X11_DI12
X11_DI13 = if (X11_DI13 != X11_DI13_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI13_RAW else X11_DI13
X11_DI14 = if (X11_DI14 != X11_DI14_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI14_RAW else X11_DI14
X11_DI15 = if (X11_DI15 != X11_DI15_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI15_RAW else X11_DI15
X11_DI16 = if (X11_DI16 != X11_DI16_RAW for EntprellZeit ms) then X11_DI16_RAW else X11_DI16
MVB_Valid = Port_463_valid and Port_464_valid and Port_465_valid and Port_466_valid and Port_467_valid and Port_468_valid and Port_509_valid
Lifesign_Diag = if msec500Tick then Lifesign_Diag +1 else Lifesign_Diag
Input_Fault = stateIo_5_HbTimeout or stateIo_5_Failure or stateIo_5_DataTimeout
Lifesign_State = if msec500Tick then Lifesign_State +1 else Lifesign_State
Lifesign_SW = if msec500Tick then Lifesign_SW +1 else Lifesign_SW
V_BEST = if (Vehicle_Speed.valid) then Vehicle_Speed else V_BEST
odometer = if (km_Counter_Vehicle.changed) then km_Counter_Vehicle else odometer
dailyDistance = if (km_Counter_Vehicle.changed) then dailyDistance + 0.05 else dailyDistance
upcomingConfiguration = if ((Config_run_status_256 for 2s) or (Config_run_status_512 for 2s)) then 1 else upcomingConfiguration

requested256 = if (requested256 and requested512) then 0 else (if (upcomingConfiguration and ((Config_request_256.valid and Config_request_256 and !Config_request_512) for 2s)) then 1 else requested256)

requested512 = if (requested256 and requested512) then 0 else (if (upcomingConfiguration and ((Config_request_512.valid and Config_request_512 and !Config_request_256) for 2s)) then 1 else requested512)
MVB_ConfigSignal = if (!statePreformatting and requested256 and !requested512) then 1 else if (!statePreformatting and !requested256 and requested512) then 2 else MVB_ConfigSignal
eth0Ip = if (MVB_ConfigSignal == 1) then "172.8.0.14" else if (MVB_ConfigSignal == 2) then "172.8.0.15" else eth0Ip
eth0DHCP = if (MVB_ConfigSignal > 0) then false else eth0DHCP
eth0Commit = if (upcomingConfiguration == 1 and (MVB_ConfigSignal.changed)) then 1 else eth0Commit
upcomingConfiguration = if(upcomingConfiguration for 80s) then 0 else upcomingConfiguration
requested256 = if(requested256 for 80s) then 0 else requested256
requested512 = if(requested512 for 80s) then 0 else requested512
stateWarning = stateMvbMissingSignal or stateFramBufferFull or stateDataDiscardedOnPrimaryStore or stateDataDiscardedOnSecondaryStore or stateFillingLevel_80 or stateMvBusError
stateError = stateStoreNotOperational or statePrimaryInactive or stateSecondaryInactive or stateRecordingError or stateStoreError or stateIo_5_HbTimeout or stateIo_5_Failure or stateIo_5_DataTimeout
MVB_TIMEDATE = if (Timedate.valid and Timezone.valid) then (Timedate - (Timezone*3600)) else MVB_TIMEDATE
stateSyncSystemTime = if (Timedate.valid) then (not stateSyncSystemTime for 2 s) else (if (minuteTick) then true else false)
Fuellstand_Rekorderspeicher = if numberOfActiveFiles > 0 then 100 - (storeFreeFiles * 100 / numberOfActiveFiles) else 0
